Requirements

Python 3.10+ (3.13 recommended)

pip

Virtual environment support

In Windows Command

Step 1 : Go to backend folder

cd backend

Step 2 : Create Virtual Environment 

python -m venv .venv

Step 3: Activate virtual environment

.venv\Scripts\activate

Step 4: Install dependencies

