Step 5: Check .env

Make sure .env exists and contains at least:

DATABASE_URL=sqlite:///./app.db
SECRET_KEY=your_secret_key
ALGORITHM=HS256
ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES=30

Step 6: Run the backend (correct way)

uvicorn app.main:app --reload

